Census2006|06}}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Masjed Soleyman County}}\n\n{{Portal|Iran}}\n\n[[Category:Populated places in Masjed Soleyman County]]\n\n{{MasjedSoleyman-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n|official_name =Laderazi\n|native_name =\u0644\u0627\u062f\u0631\u0627\u0632\u064a\n|settlement_type        = village\n|pushpin_map            =Iran\n|mapsize                =150px\n|subdivision_type       = [[List of countries|Country]]\n|subdivision_name = {{flag|Iran}}\n|subdivision_type1 =[[Provinces of Iran|Province]]\n|subdivision_name1 =[[Khuzestan Province|Khuzestan]]\n|subdivision_type2 =[[Counties of Iran|County]]\n|subdivision_name2 = [[Masjed Soleyman County|Masjed Soleyman]]\n|subdivision_type3 =[[Bakhsh]]\n|subdivision_name3 =[[Central District (Masjed Soleyman County)|Central]]\n|subdivision_type4 =[[Rural Districts of Iran|Rural District]]\n|subdivision_name4 =[[Jahangiri Rural District|Jahangiri]]\n|leader_title           = \n|leader_name            = \n|established_title      =\n|established_date       = \n|area_total_km2           = \n|area_footnotes           = \n|population_as_of         = 2006\n|population_total =49\n|population_density_km2   =auto\n|timezone               = [[Iran Standard Time|IRST]]\n|utc_offset             = +3:30\n|timezone_DST           = [[Iran Daylight Time|IRDT]]\n|utc_offset_DST         = +4:30\n|coordinates            = {{coord|32|04|42|N|49|11|32|E|region:IR|display=inline,title}}\n|elevation_m            = \n|area_code              = \n|website                = \n|footnotes              =\n}}\n'''Laderazi''' ({{lang-fa|\u0644\u0627\u062f\u0631\u0627\u0632\u064a}}, also [[Romanize]]d as '''L\u0101der\u0101z\u012b'''; also known as '''Chahsmen Ali''', '''Chashmeh-i-\u2018Ali''', '''Cheshmeh \u2018Al\u012b''', and '''Cheshmeh \u2018Al\u012b M\u016bchk\u0101n''')<ref>{{GEOnet3|-3072720|Laderazi}}</ref> is a village in [[Jahangiri Rural District]], in the [[Central District (Masjed Soleyman 